{"tid":1893092,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「思覺失調」:工聯會要求新一份財政預算案全民派錢1萬元","createTime":"2020-02-23T04:14:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T05:08:57.000Z","uid":117386,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"10538c030a26fa9d823600c22ca055273faefd10","tid":1893092,"uid":117386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T04:14:48.000Z","msg":"一批工聯會代表到政府總部外請願，要求新一份財政預算案全民派錢1萬元，又要求政府引用條例，禁止商戶炒賣防疫用品。<br />\n<br />\n工聯會立法會議員麥美娟說，現時經濟轉差，失業率上升，要求政府盡快落實失業援助金，她又批評勞工及福利局局長羅致光，指援助金批核需一年的說法「離地」。<br />\n<br />\n有人質疑建制派早前於財委會反對政府派1萬元，麥美娟澄清，當日只是表決是否處理財委會會議程序37A的臨時動議，而當日首要目的是讓300億抗疫基金通過。<br />\n<br />\n對於政府將會是15年來首次錄得財政赤字，同時又成立300億元抗疫基金，麥美娟認為，政府還有豐厚財政儲備，現時緊急關頭應善用儲備，盡快幫助市民。<br />\n<br />\n另外，她又澄清，工聯會是得到社會人士支持而生產口罩，並沒有收取政府任何利益。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1510247-20200223.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1510247-20200223.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAynr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=b30f5f19\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1510247-20200223.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ba4a3508\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1510247-20200223.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jGLH9TC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjGLH9TC.jpg&h=8e0208c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點呀？否決完又去請願，想點呀？咩事呀？係咪思覺失調？"},{"pid":"7248fd63983def62b4bb4f8e15630290f0ec4f53","tid":1893092,"uid":127929,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T04:23:48.000Z","msg":"拎大聲公去廢老區講比人知呢班人思覺失調<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7c9fefd01eb7b1b118f17e60d040c38a4226d06","tid":1893092,"uid":270951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T04:24:44.000Z","msg